https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/com.title: Morlocks (2002) #4
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/com.description: Continuing a look into the mutant urban myth! Postman. Electric Eve. Angel Dust. Shatter. Cell. Trader. Litterbug. Not so long ago, they were like anyone else -- like you and me. They had homes, families, hopes and dreams. Now, they have no choice but to go underground, where they can live in peace. But before they do that, this group of extraordinarily powered -- but still fragile -- people must face a squadron of Sentinels -- and the final goodbye to the lives they're leaving behind!
